{
  "chapter": 59,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十九回「鱼肠剑」。铁网帮红衣女子携帮众余小毛追索芮玮误杀帮众之过，提出以命抵命或比武两种赔法。芮玮选比武，红衣女子以鱼肠剑削断缚龙索为其解缚。芮玮先胜余小毛，再与红衣女子交手，剑法被破后以无敌剑反击，危急间拍飞自己的玄铁木剑以救对方，红衣女子亦以鱼肠剑截断长剑，二人险些同归于尽。红衣女子将鱼肠剑赠予芮玮，并转赠欧阳龙年之船为人情，又展示玄龟集令欧阳龙年知芮玮并未得书。芮玮携叶青乘小舟离去，简怀萱、呼哈娜追赶不及。芮玮回顾半年来携叶青寻父仇，得知真正凶手为黑堡堡主林三寒，但因林琼菊之故迟迟未往山西。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "哼！不管过失杀，有心杀，杀人就该赔偿！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "姑娘说怎么赔法？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有两种赔法。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "哪两种赔法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "一种赔法以命抵命，你虽打死我两名帮众，就以你一命相抵马马虎虎算了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "这个芮某办不到，芮某若是存心杀死贵帮帮众，以命抵命没有话说，可是芮某并非有心，而是失手误杀……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "第一种赔法，你是不答应哪？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "第一种赔法恕难从命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那只有第二种赔法啦。这第二种赔法你既有本领杀死我帮帮众，就请你再凭本领维护自家的生命！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "这话怎么说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我请余小毛替两位被杀的帮众复仇，你若能与余小毛平手可保一命，但仍要以金钱赔偿死者，你要是不能与余小毛平手，而败在他的手中，只有仍请你遵照第一种赔法啦。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "我要是败在姑娘属下手中自然难逃一死，第一种赔法不得不遵，倘若是在下不但不败，反而胜了贵属下余小毛，那怎么说？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那不可能！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "如此说来，姑娘认定在下十成有九成会败？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不错，我说你能与余小毛平手已是十分难得，放眼天下能与姑娘属下余小毛斗个平手的，能有何人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "倘若芮某与贵属下纵然是平手，亦算失败如何？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你倒认定能胜过余小毛啦？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "speaker_name": "余小毛",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "他奶奶的，动手吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "姓芮的，姑娘佩服你豪气可嘉，你要是真能胜过余小毛，我不但不要你任何赔偿，而且必有重赏。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "重赏不必，倒是请你们速离此地，免得防碍在下与欧阳先生的私事。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "适才我见过你与夙昔称霸四海的海龙王过招，莫非你们之间有什么过节？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "这过节正要了结被贵帮骚扰，说来贵帮对芮某尚有不是之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那姑娘在此先告歉了，这么着，你要是胜过余小毛，这过节姑娘替你们了结，谅那老匹夫不敢不买姑娘的账。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "多谢姑娘，在下与欧阳先生的过节自会了结，现在不必多言，贵属下等的不耐，请他就动手吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "姓芮的，你不要太狂啊？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要想胜余小毛也有道理，因咱们并未见过你的真功夫，双方较量，真章自现，可是你双手不解束缚，难不成这样相斗吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "并非芮某不自量力，实因束缚在下双手的是天下闻名的缚龙索，除非魔岛岛主难有人解，这是不得已之事，望姑娘谅解此点。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "缚龙索这名字听家父说过，果然无人解，可是不见得难得到本姑娘。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我帮属下与人较艺不能占这个大便宜，芮公子，在末比较之前，姑娘先与你解除束缚如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "不可，此人身怀玄龟集，有不世奇功，姑娘要是解开他的束缚，贵属下定然难是他的敌手！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "我不相信他怀有玄龟集。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "真的啊！玄龟集为天下奇书，你要不信，轻易解开他的束缚，后果一定对姑娘大大不利。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "我说不信就不信，要你啰嗦什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "姑娘好意在下心领，但不必再麻烦姑娘了，此索纵有断金削铁的宝刀亦难割断，在下手上功夫未见高明，只要贵属下能胜过在下足上功夫，芮玮再非其敌了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮公子，你虽说纵有宝刀利刃也割不断缚龙索，可是姑娘的宝刃非通常的宝刃，通常的宝刃能削铁如泥，我这宝刃不但能削铁如泥而且能刺穿任何奇坚的宝石。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "那是什么宝刃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "姑娘这把宝刃名叫鱼肠剑。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "果真是鱼肠剑！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我解开你的束缚，并非安下什么好心，你不要谢我，余小毛，现在可以动手了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "speaker_name": "余小毛",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "尽躲算那门呀？有本领面对面打他妈的几招，再躲是龟孙子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "text": "好，我不躲就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "speaker_name": "余小毛",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那你站稳啦。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "text": "受伤没有？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "speaker_name": "余小毛",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "还好，还好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "text": "你不是芮公子对手，退下吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "speaker_name": "余小毛",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "小姐，让我再试试，他掌法不见高明。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "text": "掌法虽不高明，内力却远胜过你，你临机不会应变，要想胜他势非可能。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "姑娘，你也不是他的对手，也退下吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮公子，你已胜了，姑娘想向你讨教一二。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "天下再厉害的剑法能守得住我的攻势吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你……你……没死……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "没死啊！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "这本书挡在胸前，是故仅刺进一寸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不止刺进一寸，起码三寸以上。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "不妨事了，姑娘剑术高强，在下承认失败。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不，你的剑术比我高，是我输了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "speaker_name": "余小毛",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子大德，余小毛替小姐叩谢大恩。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_xiao_mao",
      "text": "在下有何恩德可言，倒应在下向贵帮小姐，叩谢饶命之恩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好啦，你们不要客气，说来总是我的不对，无故生出好胜之心，这场比赛算不分胜负，可是芮公子胜了余小毛却是事实，那两名帮众之死，也不要公子赔啦。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "在下失手杀贵帮帮众，道义上要负责任，芮某至少要赔偿死者家属的金钱。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "咱们不再妨碍公子与欧阳先生的私事，就此告辞。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你为了救我拍飞自家的兵刃，现已沉落大海无法打捞，我以这把鱼肠剑赔你好吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "不好，不好，剑是我自己拍落，哪要姑娘赔。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要不收，就是不愿与我交个朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "既然你坚决不收，我已送出不能再收回……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "此物我已掷出，再算不得我的东西，公子千万不要还我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "此剑虽短，却能飞剑伤人百丈外，公子善自珍视，以公子内力，剑身之轻灵，不难练成伤人百丈外的绝技。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "姑娘以重宝相赠，在下多谢。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么赠不赠呀，是你自己抢回算不得相赠，说到相赠我倒真应该送你一点东西……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "为什么要送我东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我说过你若能战胜余小毛必有重赏，重赏什么呢？像你这种大侠客任何东西也看不上眼，啊！对于！我就送你一个人情吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "人情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这艘船欧阳先生说过赔我，可是我总不好意思要他当年横行四海的标志，我转送给你，你也不会要这么个破船，这人情就由你去做，他若不领情，你就把它砸个大窟窿，沉在海底。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "好吧，这个人情我收下了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮公子，我有一事相求，不知你愿不愿意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "什么事？只要我能办到，一定愿意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "家父有件难题，不能解决，希公子一年后驾临敝帮相助家父解决可好？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "一年后我必定到贵帮一行，但是在下能力薄弱，能不能帮助令尊实在难说，到时若无帮助，尚请姑娘原谅。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "只要公子莅临，家父的难题一定迎刃而解。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "好吧，一年后拜访贵帮时再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那么小女子告辞了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "红衣女子",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "欧阳先生不要忘了，此船我已移赠芮公子，还有你不要再为难芮公子，你们所说的玄龟集，并不在他身上，你看，这是不是你们要的东西？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_hong_yi_nv_zi",
      "text": "玄龟集！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "现在你不会再怀疑我私藏玄龟集了吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "叶青在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她安好如故，你回答我一个问题就告诉你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "什么问题，快说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你既然没有得到玄龟集，为何功力陡增？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "因为我吃了一种怪鱼，功力不由陡增。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么地方有这种怪鱼？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "恕难奉告。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不说，我也不说。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "亏你年纪一大把，说话讲不讲信用！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "为人在世当然要讲信用！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "说得好，你的一个问题我已回答，叶青在哪里还不说吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "你再不说，我立时将这艘船毁了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我说可以，但这艘船仍是我的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "你以为我希罕这艘破船吗，哼！我只要一叶扁舟，你把叶青交出，我立时偕叶青乘扁舟离去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你当真离开这艘大船？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "我不像你，说话放屁一般。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要离开，送你的小船上一定什物俱备。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "叶青在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "就在里面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这一觉睡得好长。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "青儿，咱们离开这儿。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我怎么睡在这儿？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 449,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "蒋老前辈帮助那坏老头为恶，太不应该了，也好，咱们离开这儿，永远不要再见他们。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蒋老前辈，晚辈去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，大哥……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "他与姓叶的那丫头要离开这艘大船。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 59,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    }
  ],
